# PR descriptions — mechanics & SRD

When a PR changes **game rules behavior** (dice, rolls, position/effect, XP, stress, assist, group actions, sessions, advancement):

- Add a **References** line citing `docs/1(800)-Bizarre SRD.md` (section or keywords).
- If behavior **intentionally differs** from the SRD, say so in one sentence.

Pure UI/refactor/infra PRs can state **“No mechanics change”** or skip References.
